 serve as a useful guide for efficiently predicting and\ndesigning materials or artificial systems owning exotic geometric nodal\nstructures of energy bands simply based on structure symmetries.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Feb 2021 17:57:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-14"}
