}}$. Besides, with further assumptions of regularity\nand existence of negative moment for $\\psi_{\\rho}$, we moreover show that the\nabove convergence in expectation can be strengthened to an almost sure\nconvergence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Feb 2021 22:42:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-22"}
