ncontrol has been tested on a real building cluster in Ludvika, Sweden. The\nstudy results show that the developed control can increase the cluster-level\ndaily renewable self-consumption rate by 19% and meanwhile reduce the daily\nelectricity bills by 36% compared with the conventional controls.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Feb 2021 08:21:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-22"}
