 free verbal\nrecall is one of the main differences. Reading skill level seems to be an\nimportant confounding variable. Participants would generally prefer if the test\nis conducted in a medical office rather than at a patient's home so that\nsomeone is present for support and the result can be discussed directly.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Feb 2021 14:03:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-22"}
