cting\nthe information needed for the selection from portal APIs. OSS producers can\nbenefit from our results by checking if they are providing all the information\ncommonly required by potential adopters...\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Feb 2021 15:18:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 4 Feb 2022 09:59:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-07"}
